s2 = RSS/(n - p) // Simplify\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"af7bec66-a320-4032-9598-9f64b855e6c8"],

Cell["Expectation[s2, udists]", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"120dfa8f-7eec-4835-83ff-ad9664e49a37"],

Cell["\<\
tmp = Block[{sigma = 2},
   dist = TransformedDistribution[(n - p) s2/sigma^2, ndists];
   RandomVariate[dist, 10000]];
